Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Pre===================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依附于惯性生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床 上班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭 睡觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是任由身体再现它的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.80,0:00:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害自己般地拼命工作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直努力去忘记一切 罔顾一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈崎君 这就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.49,0:00:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还差一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯干这么多我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这么不停地工作 身体会垮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盂兰盆节你也没休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我只是喜欢这么干着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不偶尔歇歇 我会被政府盯上的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下班后和休息日都令人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了消磨时间而花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼光投向现实时 便觉得会完全垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌这个小镇…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也没有离开小镇另作打算的门路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是舍弃了思考生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不愿去想…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都想忘却掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得一切都错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与她相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往 结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得这一切…都错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================OP===================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:54.37,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}熟悉的坡道上 却已不见你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:03:00.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}柔和的阳光 透过树叶投下斑点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:05.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}我独自一人 伫立在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:12.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}回顾着那些 温暖的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:20.71,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}只有你 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:26.78,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}在变幻的时间中 永驻我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:34.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}风吹而过 泪水渗眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:41.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}你的身影 已变得更远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:43.70,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}任何时候都不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:45.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}哪怕一切的一切全部改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.08,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}不忘记那一件 那一件
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}稀松平常之事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:51.57,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}终会让你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:54.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}那被光芒包裹着的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}守护 守护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:59.89,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)\be1}直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================Text===================
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.07,0:04:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉由心底的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破烂才能重塑外形的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人是无法完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已知晓这些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.80,0:04:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我 本不是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起哀伤的事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个世界本身哀伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快这里就会一片雪白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:05:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到我不能动了…就会换成你孤身一人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 还在休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一个人就过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面很乱 我收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天很热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行 偶尔要到外面振奋精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 芳野先生也经常对我这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这么热的天一个人出去也有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 我偶尔也会想和年轻人约会的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 找除我之外的人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也又帅气又善良 是我喜欢的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在早苗面前只会孩子气…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变化很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不常路过车站吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带的确…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也这个夏天能有连续的休假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:07:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司那边总是叫我「休假休假」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 要不要去哪玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我们两个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真让人心动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这次还是大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 快点 去喝果汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦 这么跑会吵到别人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧 秋生也好久没和朋也喝酒了 很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会考虑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是早苗 旅游的事想好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没去想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我过会儿再打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么催啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有想好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败给早苗了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 同意了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周后半请假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和星期天加在一起歇四天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会和公司说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我很迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在再去回绝 又会辜负早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就已把各种事情都硬塞给早苗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然有急事 我和秋生要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不用那么紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗和大叔都出去了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.87,0:11:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人没跟你说什么就走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去旅游
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为早苗和大叔都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说你一个人去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和早苗和阿秋一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是什么情况啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年来 汐完全交给早苗和大叔带了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼儿园的入园典礼和七五三时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:14.62,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七五三：小汐的情况下指三岁时的11月15日去神社参拜祈福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都在不管不顾地继续工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗时不时会带汐来见我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我都没怎么正视过她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得躲得很好么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全暴露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来 别老站那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:13:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…大概大叔和早苗晚上会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天就乖乖等着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔和早苗回来了就能去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就一个人玩着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个男孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全因为你乱跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿这个玩的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:14:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跌倒时摔坏了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龟先生好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有强力胶的话能修好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着 我帮你粘上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下点裂痕…不过也不显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶干下来之前别动它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然车轮会黏住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她懂没懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:14:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了胶干前别动的么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这车轮已经动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修不好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修不了 死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 扔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买点什么回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.83,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的话 我随便买点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀冈崎先生好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢 小汐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和爸爸买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说现在没住在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人要独自把孩子养大 会很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但经常会见面的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然见不到还是会寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说都是父女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说 说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小汐 拜拜喽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 一个人吃没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.50,0:17:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 胡椒么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 没那个成不了炒饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍着吃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 早苗应该也教过别挑食的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃早苗做的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去掉胡椒就好么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是去掉胡椒很难吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭？只吃白饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我倒是清闲了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒饭配白饭真是奇怪的组合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有菜的话 看着就像我在欺负你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七味粉么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.15,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七味粉：撒在饭上一起食用的调味粉 开胃用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.17,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不回来了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人就做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使劲游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在游泳池呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸会划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人就做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老这么得意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一个人就能做到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去…旅游吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 两人去行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吗 是和我一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗和大叔都不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 两个人都不回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧 就我们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没忘东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关好门了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 出发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前见汐时 旁边总是有早苗或大叔的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我们两人同行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这在汐出生后的五年间 还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:22:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 到底是要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================ED===================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:26.07,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}双眼凝视着 流动的云朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:32.99,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}心中感受着 天空变幻的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:41.18,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伫立不前的我们 察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.32,0:22:48.20,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}这变迁的世界编织出的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:55.44,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}伸出的指尖 不断寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.44,0:23:04.13,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那恒久不变的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.35,0:23:11.69,ed2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起的手中火炬闪亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:19.42,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那是通向明天的小小路标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:26.75,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}现在也在不断回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:34.28,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}那一天的话语 终将化为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.43,0:23:39.04,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,500)}推动我前行
