Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.05,0:23:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹注意下影响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.37,0:23:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.89,0:23:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去厕所时要说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:23:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
